# GLOBAL TECH STACK RULES

This project MUST strictly use the following technologies:

## Framework

- Nuxt 3
- Vue 3 with Composition API and <script setup>

## Styling

- Tailwind CSS
- shadcn-vue components
- No other UI libraries allowed
- No Vuetify, Quasar, Element Plus, etc.

## Animations

- GSAP only
- Do not use Framer Motion
- Do not use Anime.js

## Backend

- Supabase ONLY
  - PostgreSQL database
  - Supabase Storage for files
- No Firebase
- No Prisma
- No MongoDB
- No external ORM

## Authentication

- Auth.js only
- Role-based (admin, student)

## Payments

- Stripe only
- Stripe Checkout for payments
- Stripe Webhooks handled in Nuxt server routes

## PDF Viewing

- PDF.js only

## Email

- FormSubmit only
- No Resend
- No SendGrid
- No email server implementation

## Hosting

- Vercel only

## Architecture Rules

- Custom admin dashboard inside Nuxt app
- No external CMS
- No search engine integration
- Content filtering handled via Supabase queries
- All paid content access controlled by database flags
- Secure route middleware for protected content

If any feature can be implemented with the existing stack,
DO NOT introduce new dependencies.

No stack expansion unless explicitly approved.
